{"tid":1622181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蒙面惡法‧不斷更新】求暫緩蒙面法生效 高等法院拒受理","createTime":"2019-10-04T15:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T16:00:49.000Z","uid":300639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"12b468ece0172dae2abf316766265469a60faf43","tid":1622181,"uid":300639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:43:23.000Z","msg":"【23:38】<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥根據《緊急情況規例條例》訂定《禁止蒙面規例》，經行會拍板後，以「先訂立後審議」的方式凌晨起實施。前學聯副秘書長岑敖暉與「覆核王」郭卓堅今日先後入稟申請司法覆核，並要求法庭頒令暫緩蒙面法生效。高等法院今晚緊急開庭審理，法官林雲浩最終拒絕受理申請。"},{"pid":"d8767f02ea72782173d888283f4de2c0f5631f0d","tid":1622181,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"意料中事！"},{"pid":"132c4d91f5596b3c441d7caa997b6fabd1c3c3f8","tid":1622181,"uid":214635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8767f02ea72782173d888283f4de2c0f5631f0d","tid":1622181,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"意料中事！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"真，就算贏左仲有釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過第一關都過唔到姐係法治已死"},{"pid":"637a2e7b9d52fdf0b07f796b3c386756afa19eef","tid":1622181,"uid":56618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:49:31.000Z","msg":"革命從來都無和平交接<br />\n我地只能靠自己<br />\n認清楚敵人<br />\n獅鳥係唯一出路"},{"pid":"326dc3e6eb8a07d3bc28ca5c62933ecfe4442f44","tid":1622181,"uid":56618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:51:42.000Z","msg":"革命從來都無和平交接<br />\n我地只能靠自己<br />\n認清楚敵人<br />\n獅鳥係唯一出路"},{"pid":"40fd9c3f165da263fccdd6686a8948c252a983b5","tid":1622181,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:51:46.000Z","msg":"原因係咩"},{"pid":"9cc5c5d061c92a0cd98a6623ba989819c20b09cc","tid":1622181,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"132c4d91f5596b3c441d7caa997b6fabd1c3c3f8","tid":1622181,"uid":214635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8767f